&lt;p&gt;The post holder will provide strategic advice on the health of local looked after children. This post will provide clinical leadership for looked after children and care leavers including those undergoing adoption across Hull and East Riding Clinical Commissioning Groups and their health economies, enabling the delivery of statutory duties . The post holder will also contribute to the Statutory/Neurodevelopmental clinical service. The timetable is flexible, and can be modified to reflect the special interests and expertise of the appointee&lt;/p&gt;
